 Homework-Whisper â€” Realtime Chat (OTP auth + images)

A minimal, production-style chat app built with Vite + React + Socket.IO + Express + Prisma (SQLite).
Login via email OTP (dev-friendly), send text or images (drag & drop / paste), see realtime updates, and delete your own messages.

